Node_module - Extra library and packages
src - Our source code
public - Public assets like html and images
.gitignore - Files to be ignored by git
package.json - Manages project dependencies and scripts
package-lock.json - Keeps track of exact dependency versions
vite.config.js - Configures the Vite build tool
index.html - The main entry point for our web application
App.jsx - The main component of our application
main.jsx - Renders the App component to the DOM


Dom - Document object model (HTML representation of the web page)
Components - Reusable UI building blocks

? - is a ternary operator shortcut for if else 
=== equality Operator it checks if both value and type is the same
=> - Arrow function
The parameter is a variable that receives a value when the function is called.